name: Coding Fractals
description:
Generative artwork exploring monochromatic and the emergent effect of stacking simple shape, random monochromatic glyphs ranging from skull white to ink black, scattered amongst an eternal sea of shades of grey, representing the steps on the road to understanding.
All artworks are created using custom algorithms in processing. After the process of making images, these images have been turned into text coding art with artificial intelligence.
